section_title: Rate of interest on Government debt to the Banks of England and Ireland.
†Internal regulations and stock of Bank of England.
section_text: 7 1 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  2 Notwithstanding the repeal of any enactment by this Act the capital stock of the Bank of England as existing at the passing of this Act shall be subject to the enactments so far as unrepealed which relate to stock of the Bank of England, and the holders of the stock shall be members of the corporation of the Bank of England.
